/**
 * @description Returns {String} of HTTP path requests
 */
const MAIN_PATH = '/api/employees'

export default class Employees {
   static __MAIN_PATH = '/employees'
   static GET_API_INFO = MAIN_PATH + '/api_info'
   static GET_EMPLOYEES = MAIN_PATH + '/'
   static GET_EMPLOYEE_BY_ID = MAIN_PATH + '/id/id='
   static GET_EMPLOYEE_BY_NAME = MAIN_PATH + '/name/name='
   static GET_EMPLOYEE_BY_ROLE = MAIN_PATH + '/role/role='
   static CREATE_EMPLOYEE = MAIN_PATH + '/'
   static UPDATE_EMPLOYEE = MAIN_PATH + '/'
   static DELETE_EMPLOYEE_BY_ID = MAIN_PATH + '/id='

}
